g src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc59f53310c7ab6dc8545eece5a63efe4e61eafe","tid":189900,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4cbd0a7556e8c82e4569d87e298f0e7fa72124","tid":189900,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個名就係你故事？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試my去接受呢件事<br />\n諗下有咩係從中得到<br />\n再慢慢後悔下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經經歷晒以上步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔硬訓無意思<br />\n聽晚後晚又黎過<br />\n祝你搵到啱你既避風港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d10f1b448a19e55beaba9babd67043475986014","tid":189900,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放低手機  數羊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實要點數 我愈數愈精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aeacfe800678e0009f55521ee6c8b26ccf237c1","tid":189900,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ce9c63314585e5b02d7065870acd5a92884bb0","tid":189900,"uid":49363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:25:54.000Z","msg":"加