啲眼淚都係自己流<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱開始嗰陣喊咗一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人一無嘢做就會諗起佢之後就喊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 所以會夾硬搵野做 但其實做乜都無心情 一啲都唔enjoy 因係為左攝住啲時間 一停落黎又係喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c5330210149d5b496003cf4905485801a3faac","tid":189900,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲玩電話點會訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n瘋狂斬眼訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩完喇 而家試下瞓先 希望唔會一粒鐘後又見到我出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024cee196d021c260156c9accd1724239ec7c452","tid":189900,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加油呀 你會捱過的<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我每日都失眠 15年了..</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n15年... 點捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經習慣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要加油呀 如果你想的話 可以陪你傾下計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打唔洗番工? 日日失眠咁點算? 我有時失眠完第二日個頭勁暈 跟住第二晚就好好瞓 第三晚又再失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家唔洗 之前就算要番工 都失眠 放工返屋企恰陣 之後又眼光光等天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經試過失眠搞到要SL 落床果下已經頭暈 我驚放工恰完夜晚會瞓唔著 但就算唔恰都瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29a19f8d6fb1730794f71550d0d6092adc484aa","tid":189900,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩事分手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢搵番個ex 詳情就唔再講喇 係我自己天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b1631bbbb895bf3122315a1e70055629fc1da6","tid":189900,"uid":89478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩日前先失眠完 今晚又失眠 枕頭又喊到濕晒 乜都唔諗啲眼淚都會自己流 點先可以快啲瞓著? <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無撚用 你條女雞黎 諗乜鬼野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8e421193df246078f6218282d728ac87281927","tid":189900,"uid":51145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>放低手機  數羊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實要點數 我愈數愈精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幻想啲一羊一隻一隻咁跳過   數字其次  放鬆同放低手機最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n數綿羊其實因為sheep sleep差唔多發音，數數下就會sleep到<br />\n樓主試下數水餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n數水餃唔會好肚餓咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7187185df0b5dc512ed29a208053ff7748f37d1a","tid":189900,"uid":69202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加油呀 你會捱過的<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我每日都失眠 15年了..</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n15年... 點捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經習慣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要加油呀 如果你想的話 可以陪你傾下計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打唔洗番工? 日日失眠咁點算? 我有時失眠完第二日個頭勁暈 跟住第二晚就好好瞓 第三晚又再失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家唔洗 之前就算要番工 都失眠 放工返屋企恰陣 之後又眼光光等天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經試過失眠搞到要SL 落床果下已經頭暈 我驚放工恰完夜晚會瞓唔著 但就算唔恰都瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下攬住公仔訓呀<br />\n都係訓唔到 我可以陪你 應該係你陪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caeeeed03e61681802fcdfd50d879e89fadd6d51","tid":189900,"uid":32620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲玩電話點會訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n瘋狂斬眼訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩完喇 而家試下瞓先 希望唔會一粒鐘後又見到我出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> goodnight"},{"pid":"720876473844c6472bdacdd67b380b64bac4dbcd","tid":189900,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:54:38.000Z","msg":"拎紙筆寫低晒啲諗法出嚟 諗到咩就寫 有科學根據可以幫到失眠<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bdd44bb350c74185b852a1ccc4903748403084","tid":189900,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加油呀 你會捱過的<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我每日都失眠 15年了..</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1