8d5170c7ce7429194553","tid":189900,"uid":4010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:07:57.000Z","msg":"食支煙冷靜下"},{"pid":"ae0b0e51093aca223a97e12c7af9822e16fd3dc1","tid":189900,"uid":69202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n回復唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日得閒就去stalk下佢ig諗下以前同佢啲嘢睇下同佢個chatting box<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做呢啲野.. 一定喊到收唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗住喊多陣就會停點知停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係 有時夾硬停左 迫自己唔諗野 但係啲眼淚都係自己流<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱開始嗰陣喊咗一個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人一無嘢做就會諗起佢之後就喊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 所以會夾硬搵野做 但其實做乜都無心情 一啲都唔enjoy 因係為左攝住啲時間 一停落黎又係喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本專心唔到做其他嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依段時期係最痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6cd98f7514d3223dec2f694c5b6367c91c3280","tid":189900,"uid":81220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:14:52.000Z","msg":"好老土講 真係得時間同下一個岩既人先完全解決到<br />\n不過你可以試下瘋狂睇綜藝節目<br />\n揀好笑既睇 舊都無所謂 專心睇 就會無諗咁多野<br />\n當時我係睇running man同無限挑戰<br />\n個時既rm好好笑 我用一個月日煲夜煲由零追上直播（百零集）<br />\n個心掛住追 都無諗咁多野 笑笑下個人都無咁澀<br />\n不過我真係一日睇十集個啲黎 日夜顛倒晒<br />\n個陣study leave 咁最後個al就緊係衰左<br />\n但都叫慢慢走左出去 <br />\n一開始我既生活完全行屍走肉 頭幾個月都唔知自己做過咩<br />\n全日都訓係床到喊 喊到攰就訓 餓到痛就食野<br />\n真係時間沖淡一切 老土到嘔<br />\n我依加搵到個好好既男朋友 所以你都要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b499f8d0b5e857e571d914683e3f450d97d22936","tid":189900,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:15:24.000Z","msg":"唔好忍 喊完就唔喊"},{"pid":"b5cabd54562da90a2d15bf9c2bf81a17dd9e2182","tid":189900,"uid":3008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:19:55.000Z","msg":"唔開心喊得出好過喊唔出 屈住屈住好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4559f89f9a21c92258f606b9d17a07c5d1df60b9","tid":189900,"uid":104214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:45:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>逼自己咪埋眼訓 千其唔好開眼 過一陣就想訓 絕對有效 之前有失眠</blockquote><br />\n呢啲真係要逼出唻 吾迫點都訓吾到"},{"pid":"619263a8c024a510ec231af66e31db2775efc1b1","tid":189900,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:50:40.000Z","msg":"見到你既經歷同狀態就好似見到自己一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7162bffe9e85167058a5be9f69b8cc2cfddb6180","tid":189900,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:56:06.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5c070870e08e4d0b74f5d4fc9e0a8566a4f72a","tid":189900,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T20:14:38.000Z","msg":"以為唱左麟右李<br />\n<br />\n加油，時間乜都沖得走"},{"pid":"3632d0e95ebbe46543840b9c63c2d07e4458b010","tid":189900,"uid":104214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T20:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為唱左麟右李<br />\n<br />\n加油，時間乜都沖得走</blockquote><br />\n經歷過就知時間真係咩都沖得走 係個下放吾低"},{"pid":"1f8367c9d9421979621c9d1ee6cf894bee83b54f","tid":189900,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T23:09:17.000Z","msg":"結果用多粒半鐘先瞓得著 岩岩比媽媽嘈醒左又瞓唔番 而家要起身番工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n估唔到竟然有咁多同路人回post 我都相信時間可以沖走一切 不過唔知要幾耐 我驚未沖走我已經頂唔順 就算睇完啲好笑嘅野 轉個頭又係喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834127a65cdc0e0595f76a21c4d7ca8e1a46d4ac","tid":189900,"uid":14272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T23:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結果用多粒半鐘先瞓得著 岩岩比媽媽嘈醒左又瞓唔番 而家要起身番工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n估唔到竟然有咁多同路人回post 我都相信時間可以沖走一切 不過唔知要幾耐 我驚未沖走我已經頂唔順 就算睇完啲好笑嘅野 轉個頭又係喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慢慢會好過來的 唔需要為人渣而唔開心 慶幸及早睇清楚一個人"},{"pid":"538b427e222943c6a5adf678672ba0e294fa20d4","tid":189900,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T23:16:23.000Z","msg":"俾咗隻豬人？<br />\n慘慘"},{"pid":"e85fdae4153e6230e6f55e83381d7998b7350f93","tid":189900,"uid":47384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:00:08.000Z","msg":"慘 我都好撚唔開心"},{"pid":"03f76b5a3797a5d9e4382315a0c4fcdf1ccb0553","tid":189900,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:24:16.000Z","msg":"有咩咁大件事"},{"pid":"ba0bf1c95182bea23442549efbbb1a5babda926c","tid":189900,"uid":36780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:28:54.000Z","msg":"喊唔係唔得 <br />\n喊係D值得喊既事到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a8349e226c104dcac426db9b452a299c14eda5","tid":189900,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:33:26.000Z","msg":"有咁多位巴絲陪你傾計"},{"pid":"c9b70d6787638b2caac0f7183b9c9e6477280d7d","tid":189900,"uid":529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:35:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p4AE2KNYA9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2